-- Bruederle Would Give Greece More Time for Reforms, Welt Reports
-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 2012-07-07T08:06:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-07/bruederle-would-give-greece-more-time-for-reforms-welt-reports.html
Rainer Bruederle, floor leader of
 Chancellor Angela Merkel ’s Free Democratic coalition partner,
said it would “make sense” to give Greece more time to
implement reforms required as part of the European Union bailout
package,  Welt am Sonntag  reported in a preview of an article
that will be published tomorrow, citing Bruederle.  To contact the reporter on this story:
